Class ExperimentRunManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.geppetto.simulation.manager.ExperimentRunManager
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IExperimentListener

    public class ExperimentRunManager
extends java.lang.Object
implements IExperimentListener
    The ExperimentRunManager is a singleton responsible for managing a queue per each user to run the experiments.

    dandromereschi, matteocantarelli
